{"tid":1038880,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】傳孟晚舟案被揭  源自滙豐內部調查","createTime":"2019-02-27T04:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T08:08:18.000Z","uid":66271,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d0fc5b76282405bab332d24daf87d95431f5144d","tid":1038880,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:33:39.000Z","msg":"《路透》報道，華為副董事長孟晚舟被加拿大當局拘捕一案，源自滙豐（00005）的內部調查，並主動向美國司法部滙報。據悉滙豐在2016年為了換取美國司法部信任，試圖解除違反美國制裁禁令的刑事指控，因此進行內部調查。最終發現華為與已出售的公司有密切關連，以及出售電訊產品予伊朗的證據。有關調查成為美國司法部提出引渡孟晚舟回美國受審的重要佐證。"},{"pid":"a5170781dd62ba8144c01eb029466bc84daa5df4","tid":1038880,"uid":6063,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:34:42.000Z","msg":"005 走鬼"},{"pid":"99614452691caf9dda4f60af455f3d51a4025e7e","tid":1038880,"uid":40272,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"習震怒"},{"pid":"6c2afbda9aaf5f8b582a37a042cce1e7b72741cd","tid":1038880,"uid":7940,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a5170781dd62ba8144c01eb029466bc84daa5df4","tid":1038880,"uid":6063,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:34:42.000Z","msg":"005 走鬼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:51:05.000Z","msg":"等冧，再趁低入市"},{"pid":"c5ce0ba303e3b94272310726d98b9043035381c8","tid":1038880,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0529ad1cf206b4fe09acfb95256329588bc247","tid":1038880,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:57:10.000Z","msg":"香港上海匯豐銀行首先是上海匯豐銀行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"467c01d7379cc71ad2c217fecd38397ff75cb9bf","tid":1038880,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eae87693d270b0cf0e58a839c54bea25d3d423